# Cursor Rules — Thane Bungalow Booking System (Root)

## Project Context
Vacation bungalow booking system for two properties in Thane, Maharashtra.
Monorepo: `/backend` (Express), `/frontend` (React), `/shared` (types).
Shared TypeScript interfaces in `/shared/types/` are the API contract source of truth.

## General Rules
- TypeScript strict mode everywhere
- Named exports only, no default exports
- kebab-case filenames, PascalCase components
- All monetary values in paise (integer), display as ₹X,XXX in frontend
- All dates stored as UTC, display as IST (Asia/Kolkata) in frontend
- Conventional commits: feat:, fix:, chore:, docs:
